Package: MLMResearch
Type: Package
Title: Multilevel Meta-Analysis Method Evaluation and Improvement
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mahmood", "Ahmad", email = "mahmood726@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: A research companion package to MLM501 that systematically evaluates modern multilevel meta-analysis methods on 501+ Cochrane review datasets. Identifies methodological flaws, tests performance across different outcome types, and develops improved methods for small-sample corrections and robust variance estimation.
